{"tid":764501,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]telegram壞鳩左","createTime":"2018-08-02T04:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T14:17:32.000Z","uid":72562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2a2caebd85e0f802c963d0d7a91f31d8eeb740","tid":764501,"uid":72562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"今朝電話無喇喇熄左<br />\n開返之後telegram就開始怪怪地<br />\n私chat ok<br />\ngp chat就睇唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聯絡人list閃下閃下<br />\n撳到入去都係一片空白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但又有通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後仲擅自改左我background <br />\n聯絡人個名冇左<br />\n私chat 唔可以引用回覆<br />\n睇相睇入去就一片黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最恐怖嘅事我諗住web版開<br />\nfail左兩次 佢就話我活動得太頻繁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫我遲啲再試 <br />\n但遲咗成個鐘都唔撚入到 會唔會之後都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我去咗睇吓點樣聯絡telegram <br />\n只係搵到fb 已經講咗咩事但係都無人應我<br />\n<br />\n利申 冇backup <br />\ndelapp record會冇哂？<br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1449d2e7f007e1991f53a962d4c339848b6650fb","tid":764501,"uid":72562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c9fe47fe607bcb4d9b3795d6819ea418f059060","tid":764501,"uid":33420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"有冇試下logout再login呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59594cb285a9c2708ceae592d609d46e7e614aeb","tid":764501,"uid":33420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67fed53fb7f77ab37015cf333a8d9a3daaa5b47","tid":764501,"uid":72562,"like":0,"dislik